<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="106" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="106">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="19" pageNumber="106">Mentum bearing paired foveae; protibia with apicolateral notch; dorsal surface typically with isodiametric microsculpture; pronotum subquadrate; i8 not markedly diverted around Eo5-6 (Fig. 1B); ARG elongate, hooked anteriorly into or effaced laterad of Ed4 (Fig. 1D).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
